snippet: The J. M. Smucker Company posted better-than-expected quarterly results and forecast strong growth for the rest of the year.
abstract: JM Smucker Company posts better-than-expected quarterly earnings of $110.9 million, compared to 111.5 million in the same period a year earlier; forecasts strong growth for the rest of 2012.
lead_paragraph: The J. M. Smucker Company posted better-than-expected quarterly results and forecast strong growth for the rest of the year.

headline.main: Smucker Gains 5 Percent After a Strong Quarter
headline.print_headline: Smucker Gains 5 Percent After a Strong Quarter
